<item>
            <title>[LU-10277] DNE3: allow &apos;lfs mkdir&apos; to create directory on MDS which has more space</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10277</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On DNE system, it will be good to allow &apos;&lt;tt&gt;lfs mkdir&lt;/tt&gt;&apos; to create directory on MDT which has more free space. In this way, user doesn&apos;t need to care much about balance between MDTs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
